# KUZAYA map style (baseline ‚Äî do not drift without user request)

## Google Map theme
- Source: `src/lib/googleMapBrandTheme.ts` (Snazzy-style JSON palette)
- **No `mapId` on `<Map>`** ‚Äî Map ID disables client-side `styles`; keep JSON theme
- `mapTypeId: 'roadmap'`, background `#212121`
- Palette: land `#212121`, water `#2d4c4c`, highways `#e69138`, labels `#cccccc`
- Show: country labels, arterial/highway roads, borders
- Hide: local roads, POIs, locality/province/water labels, transit
- Region: Kenya + Rwanda only (`strictBounds: true` in `googleMapsConfig.ts`)

## Viewport & layering (z-index)
Square edges ‚Äî **no border-radius** on map viewport.
```
viewport (z1) ‚Üí inner/map (z2) ‚Üí atmosphere (z3) ‚Üí viewport-gradient (z4) ‚Üí markers (z5) ‚Üí instruments (z100)
```
- Page-transition fade: `.map-section__viewport-gradient` in `App.css` (top/bottom + radial vignette)
- Atmosphere veil/shade only when instrumented (`.map-section__atmosphere--active`)

## Atmosphere (from KUZAYA-v2 / :5177)
- `MapEarthmapTint` wired in `GeoMap.tsx` ‚Äî radial vignette on map overlay layer
- Instrumented: canvas `filter: brightness(0.68) saturate(0.82)` + stronger earthmap tint
- Top shade: always `opacity: 0.55`, full `opacity: 1` when `.map-section__atmosphere--active`
- Bottom fade: always visible (v2 gradient), no hide-when-idle

## Markers (approved approach)
- **External layer** `map-section__markers` via `GeoMarkersLayerContext` ‚Äî pins **above** gradient
- `GeoMarker.tsx`: portal to external layer + `projectLatLngToElement()` from `mapProjection.ts`
- Update on: idle, zoom, bounds/center change, resize
- **Do not** move pins back inside map-only OverlayView or stage-level experiments unless user asks
- Production pins: orange `#e85d3a` from `locations.ts`
- Voice pins: blue `#4a7c9b` from `voices.ts` / `voiceMapPlaces.ts`
- Voice coords: hub cities in `MAP_PLACES`; tiny ring offset (`radius = ring * 0.0025`) for shared hubs only ‚Äî never large linear spreads

## Pin labels (production / instrumented mode)
- Column layout: dot above label (`GeoMap.css`)
- Instrumented labels visible on both `.geo-map--instrumented` and `.map-section__markers--instrumented`
- Hover/active pins: z-index 800 via `:has(.geo-marker--hovered)`

## Dev
- Dev server: port **5173** (`strictPort: true`)
- Do not add custom country label overlays ‚Äî use Google's country labels
